{"tid":561702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年非禮女途人判囚 官：智障唔係大晒","createTime":"2018-02-15T08:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T06:52:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":311,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"472e990b0823e3c4853724b0b761a72bcba4e0d8","tid":561702,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180215/20306224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F20306224&d=IBHhdrFBJbQzXrIVFJJjuUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1a0af1a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F20306224&h=9889614f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180215/20306224</a><br />\n<br />\n青年非禮女途人判囚<br />\n官：智障唔係大晒<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180215/large/1518628019_cd96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180215%2Flarge%2F1518628019_cd96.jpg&h=5ebf4308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有12次非禮案底的被告楊楚康昨被判囚。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有多次非禮案底、曾經被受害女生形容「樣衰到嚇人」的輕度智障青年重施故技，在黃大仙非禮女途人，由對方的臀部摸至大腿，過程遭便衣警員目擊。智障男昨日承認一項非禮罪，被判囚3個月。裁判官表示明白被告智障，「但唔係大晒」，批評他非禮女性，並且教訓他一餐：「人哋可唔可以見到邊個樣衰就揼邊個呀？人哋覺得睇你唔順眼，可唔可以揼你呀？唔得呀嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被受害女生指樣衰到嚇人<br />\n<br />\n無業的被告楊楚康（19歲）有12次同類案底，靠父親的綜援金過活。主任裁判官吳蕙芳指其他智障人士也懂守法，直言被告「根本係色情狂」，批評他不工作，「游手好閒，咪胡思亂想諗吓點摸女人囉」，着他想想「人哋可唔可以摸你阿媽、家姐細妹呀？」吳官警告，若被告再犯案，必定加刑。<br />\n<br />\n案發於去年9月22日晚上7時半，被告在鳳德邨踏單車，因形迹可疑引起便衣警留意。警員發現被告在行人天橋一直尾隨一名27歲女子到碧鳳樓外，被告後來下單車衝上前，用手摸該女子的臀至大腿後逃跑，警員上前拘捕被告。<br />\n<br />\n被告於2015年兩度非禮同一名中六女生，女生作供時稱被告「特別樣衰，樣衰到嚇人，所以特別認得」。被告在該案被判入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC348/18<br />\n■記者黃幗慧"},{"pid":"33187f60a4f8dbbd1ea38a7c66b6d56e6d5e853b","tid":561702,"uid":3161,"like":237,"dislike":25,"score":212,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"靚仔過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ebc94b573d83e15dc93d7a1939bc39e1b2794d","tid":561702,"uid":119458,"like":159,"dislike":3,"score":156,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"原來色狼真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d1a6edf99e27f79e54a7816689fb0274794696","tid":561702,"uid":39215,"like":211,"dislike":3,"score":208,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"睇佢個樣都知痴撚線啦<br />\n12次案底 終生就啱架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103231cdd7df82710b169f089f3ff53db02bb470","tid":561702,"uid":87780,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:31:38.000Z","msg":"拎去打靶啦<br />\n養廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62629591531230b060deb65be53b2eabc28be8cc","tid":561702,"uid":108467,"like":9,"dislike":111,"score":-102,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"老實講，係樣衰，但唔係好撚樣衰嗰種。"},{"pid":"4bcdb1f031fad19570874f56a4796ebd5b9beab6","tid":561702,"uid":25653,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:34:47.000Z","msg":"衰多幾次就學識強姦 判咁輕 遲早出事"},{"pid":"1cf2815e0d976f6548f16115bae30bec19ffb5dc","tid":561702,"uid":28277,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33187f60a4f8dbbd1ea38a7c66b6d56e6d5e853b","tid":561702,"uid":3161,"like":237,"dislike":25,"score":212,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"靚仔過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:42:51.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"96201b593e2100e275a7cee8a6916e3814744de6","tid":561702,"uid":130879,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"有左膠保護 弱智光環你吹咩"},{"pid":"16b40989e1a478a5410bd6eef3c22eb0df49d787","tid":561702,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"