8-02-15T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"老實講，係樣衰，但唔係好撚樣衰嗰種。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執執佢根本係正常大陸仔樣"},{"pid":"f7f52e31f56d7eb46815da3719d614ac95d7fc17","tid":561702,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:38:39.000Z","msg":"攞去試藥算啦呢啲垃圾"},{"pid":"17af8f56dea62616ac7d8920c648ab2f9f831ff0","tid":561702,"uid":33643,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"在控方讀案情期間，主任裁判官吳蕙芳發現被告向兩名事主所發送的「粗口短訊」中，其中兩句「你老母&times;」被寫成「你老母西」，質疑「寫少咗個門字」，可能令句子意思完全不同，控方聽取裁判官意見後即時更正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n吳官好正"},{"pid":"05eddcdb155ed3d30a61bf5d021bad6bd753a8e4","tid":561702,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:44:49.000Z","msg":"吳青天好波"},{"pid":"519edc09388f53dc5656040313103c6571bca3d3","tid":561702,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33187f60a4f8dbbd1ea38a7c66b6d56e6d5e853b","tid":561702,"uid":3161,"like":237,"dislike":25,"score":212,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"靚仔過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5d8546102984b90501189ae9d377a39435fd0c","tid":561702,"uid":33643,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"one more<br />\n<br />\n老伯的太太和女兒昨到庭支持。主任裁判官吳蕙芳判刑時指<span style=\"color: red;\">「阿伯曳喇你」、「唔想老婆知，𠵱家乜都知晒」、「你自己都覺得醜」，老伯聽得害羞低頭。吳官又指「老公嫖妓對所有老婆都係好傷心嘅一件事」，老伯、太太和女兒聽到後相繼流淚。 </span><br />\n<br />\n老伯哭着請求輕判，吳官問他：「咁你會唔會覺得對唔住老婆？」<span style=\"color: red;\">老伯即說：「老婆我真係對你唔住！」吳官先要他提高聲量再說一遍，然後指「𠵱家唔係同我道歉」，叫他面向太太再三重複。太太聽到後哭得更厲害，並說原諒丈夫，吳官則說：「你都幾大方，幾豁達，唔係好多老婆講得出原諒佢㗎。」 </span><br />\n吳官最後充當「和事老」，叫夫妻二人<span style=\"color: red;\">「從此以後擺低件事，唔准再提，無論嗌幾多次交，唔准提」，又勸太太「唔好再有心病，相信你做得到</span>」，太太「唔」一聲答應後，便與丈夫及女兒離開法庭。 <br />\n<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a11ecd48d8456d295fed13f0c0a54665c608e09","tid":561702,"uid":25971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b83b2f5de03119f212d1392ede44c910b2077c8","tid":561702,"uid":33643,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"人哋可唔可以見到邊個樣衰就揼邊個呀？人哋覺得睇你唔順眼，可唔可以揼你呀？唔得呀嘛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 段嘢好唔正經，好似講數咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:48:15.000Z","msg":"好似陳浩南d語氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1621cd2750679278a9ba8fd428c3c78f2976d3","tid":561702,"uid":85964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62629591531230b060deb65be53b2eabc28be8cc","tid":561702,"uid":108467,"like":9,"dislike":111,"score":-102,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"老實講，係樣衰，但唔係好撚樣衰嗰種。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"你標準都好低下 係咪會覺得自己好靚仔"},{"pid":"90536771d787e929f30f4776e1dca14ab9121568","tid":561702,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"個官似番個人"},{"pid":"d7b3315ad0f66c32336b2c02598dad75ee943693","tid":561702,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://movie.supergm.net/images/20081026085410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmovie.supergm.net%2Fimages%2F20081026085410.jpg&h=790b0aa1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e782bb6084c422a3c8715098a690425aab863ad7","tid":561702,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1621cd2750679278a9ba8fd428c3c78f2976d3","t